data.description: Welcome home...A great find!! A spacious ranch freshly painted, lots of upgrades and well maintained.  Huge family room with built in cabinets and FP with natural gas logs. DR also with FP. A flex space/bonus room with vaulted ceiling would make a great home office or playroom. Separate Laundry rm and utility rm. 2018 new roof and updated appliances. Sit and relax on your large outdoor patio with corner lot. Storage building in partially fenced yard.  Convenient location to both Raleigh and Fayetteville.
